title: TA Benchamarachuthit F.C.
text: TA Benchamarachuthit Football Club (<a href="Thai%20alphabet">Thai</a> ทีเอ เบญจมราชูทิศ) is a Thai new semi professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in Tha Chang District of <a href="Chanthaburi%20Province">Chanthaburi Province</a>. They currently play in <a href="Regional%20League%20Division%202">Regional League Division 2</a> Central & Eastern in 2016.
